Three-layer pyramid model mirroring the RHT Collaborative's presentation structure:
- Layer 1 (Infrastructure): Broadband, EHR, Interop, Cloud/AI, Cybersecurity
- Layer 2 (Ecosystem): Technology, Advisors, Providers, Other partners
- Layer 3 (Solutions): Mapped to 5 CMS RHT Goals

New files:
- src/types/state-pyramid.ts — typed config interfaces for any state
- src/components/pyramid-tabs.tsx — reusable tabbed accordion component
- src/data/kentucky-pyramid-config.ts — Kentucky-specific pyramid data

Changes:
- Kentucky page rebuilt with compact header + PyramidTabs + footer
- Nav header simplified to single "Kentucky" link
- Satellite planner gets back-link breadcrumb
- Data appendix page preserved as-is

Co-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.6 <noreply@anthropic.com>
